Refactored communications part to use raw socket to avoid parsing aiohttp error message. 
List each indoor AC unit as its own device instead of listing everything in the same device
Redone the config flow to support multiple outdoor unit
Fix racing condition when controlling using the WebUI and physical control at the same time

